    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu </p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 7 (Spell Level 4)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 4</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 22 | <b>Successes:</b> 6</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 10 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 24</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, H</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You temporarily change the flexibility of your bones and skin, gaining a +4 bonus to Escape Artist and opposed Grapple checks. You may also spend a full-round action to deliver a melee touch attack at a range of up to 30 ft, stretching your limb temporarily.</p>\n\n\n\n",
